1.0.1 Metadata

1.0.1.1 Description

Dataset name: Model predictions for the 4 models

Data frame describing the model predictions of the 4 models. This data frame is generated by the study1_preprocessing.Rmd script. The values in the dataset represent similarity scores with 0 being very similar and 1 being very disimilar. These values will be used to build model RDMs for comparison with the empirical RDMs from the Causal Task and Sorting Task
